DISPOSABLE HERO:

        First select the {OPTIONS} from the main menu.  Then set the MODE
        option to {ARCADE} and set the sound sfx volume to zero.  Next
        select exit.  Now go to the highscore table, hold down the RIGHT
        MOUSE BUTTON and type "EUPHORIA".  Then press the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON
        to go back to the main menu.  Now select {OPTIONS} from the menu.
        When the options menu appears a new option will be present at the
        bottom of the list.  Select this for a cheat menu.
